  "description": "I am self-aware that a lot of my recent newsletters have been a lot of words that honestly don\u0026rsquo;t say much. They\u0026rsquo;d fully qualify as navel-gazing. It\u0026rsquo;s a time in my life for navel-gazing. The orientation is still toward bringing myself toward full participation in liberation, so I hope it\u0026rsquo;s still fascinating to read, if in a different way than my newsletters used to be. I’ve been getting more subscribers recently, so that’s reassuring. If you’ve been enjoying these letters, consider recommending them.\n",
